               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17610225-27-off134-c271" targOrder="Y" targets="t17610225-27-defend320 t17610225-27-off134 t17610225-27-verdict137"></join>
         
               <p>106. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17610225-27-defend320" type="defendantName">
                     Joseph 
                     Hunter 
                  <interp inst="t17610225-27-defend320" type="surname" value="Hunter"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-defend320" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-defend320" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , was indicted for <rs id="t17610225-27-off134" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-off134" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-off134" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing two pieces of bar-iron, value 2 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17610225-27-victim322" type="victimName">
                     Benj 
                     Taylor 
                  <interp inst="t17610225-27-victim322" type="surname" value="Taylor"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-victim322" type="given" value="Benj"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-victim322" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17610225-27-off134 t17610225-27-victim322"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17610225-27-cd135" type="crimeDate">Feb. 18</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17610225-27-off134 t17610225-27-cd135"></join>.~</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17610225-27-person323">
                  Benj 
                  Taylor 
               <interp inst="t17610225-27-person323" type="surname" value="Taylor"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-person323" type="given" value="Benj"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-person323" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a<rs id="t17610225-27-viclabel136" type="occupation">coach-tire-maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17610225-27-victim322 t17610225-27-viclabel136"></join>, last Wednesday I saw the prisoner coming out of my shop, I went and took hold of him, and he had these two pieces of bar-iron upon him, [ produced in court ] my property.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17610225-27-person324">
                  Samuel 
                  Broadbent 
               <interp inst="t17610225-27-person324" type="surname" value="Broadbent"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-person324" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-person324" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prosecutor take these two pieces of iron from the prisoner at the bar, in the street near his shop. The prisoner owned the fact in my hearing.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in his defence.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17610225-27-verdict137" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-verdict137" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17610225-27-punish138" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17610225-27-punish138" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17610225-27-defend320 t17610225-27-punish138"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
